{
  "page": "Fighting at Bitterbridge",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Fighting at Bitterbridge</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bitterbridge\" title=\"Bitterbridge\">Bitterbridge</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon of Dragonstone.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone.svg/33px-House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone.svg.png\" width=\"33\" height=\"36\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone.svg/50px-House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone.svg/66px-House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone\" title=\"House Baratheon of Dragonstone\">House Baratheon of Dragonstone</a>:</b>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Men_of_the_Reach\" title=\"Men of the Reach\">Men of the Reach</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-StannisReach_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-StannisReach-1\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Crane\" title=\"House Crane\"><img alt=\"House Crane.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/22/House_Crane.svg/20px-House_Crane.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/22/House_Crane.svg/30px-House_Crane.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/22/House_Crane.svg/40px-House_Crane.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Crane\" title=\"House Crane\">House Crane</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Florent\" title=\"House Florent\"><img alt=\"House Florent.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/House_Florent.svg/20px-House_Florent.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/House_Florent.svg/30px-House_Florent.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/House_Florent.svg/40px-House_Florent.svg.png 2x\" /></a><a href=\"/index.php/House_Florent\" title=\"House Florent\">House Florent</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlanders\" title=\"Stormlanders\">Stormlanders</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-StannisStorm_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-StannisStorm-4\">&#91;N 2&#93;</a></sup></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Tyrell.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/30px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"30\" height=\"33\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/45px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/60px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> The <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Tyrell_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Tyrell-5\">&#91;N 3&#93;</a></sup>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarly\" title=\"House Tarly\"><img alt=\"House Tarly.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/20px-House_Tarly.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/30px-House_Tarly.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/40px-House_Tarly.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarly\" title=\"House Tarly\">House Tarly</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/20px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/30px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/40px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Crane.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Crane.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/22/House_Crane.svg/20px-House_Crane.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/22/House_Crane.svg/30px-House_Crane.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/22/House_Crane.svg/40px-House_Crane.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Parmen_Crane\" title=\"Parmen Crane\">Parmen Crane</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Florent.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Florent.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/House_Florent.svg/20px-House_Florent.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/House_Florent.svg/30px-House_Florent.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/House_Florent.svg/40px-House_Florent.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Errol_Florent\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Errol Florent\">Errol Florent</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Tyrell.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/20px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/30px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/40px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Tarly.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Tarly.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/20px-House_Tarly.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/30px-House_Tarly.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarly.svg/40px-House_Tarly.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Randyll_Tarly\" title=\"Randyll Tarly\">Randyll Tarly</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown<br /> Ser Parmen Crane (POW)<br /> Ser Errol Florent (POW)</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      </td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Fighting at Bitterbridge</b> occurs during the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a> in the aftermath of the death of King <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End_(299)\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End (299)\">fall</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a> to King <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Fighting\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Fighting</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fighting_at_Bitterbridge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a> holds a great <a href=\"/index.php/Melee_at_Bitterbridge\" title=\"Melee at Bitterbridge\">melee at Bitterbridge</a> during his march toward <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> After hearing that his older brother <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis</a> has <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End_(299)\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End (299)\">besieged Storm's End</a>, Renly leaves his foot at Bitterbridge with his queen, <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and rides east with his horse to confront Stannis.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Melisandre\" title=\"Melisandre\">Melisandre</a> assassinates Renly with a <a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_child\" title=\"Shadow child\">shadow</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> however, and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a>, kills two of his fellow <a href=\"/index.php/Rainbow_Guard\" title=\"Rainbow Guard\">Rainbow Guard</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Robar_Royce\" title=\"Robar Royce\">Robar Royce</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Emmon_Cuy\" title=\"Emmon Cuy\">Emmon Cuy</a>, and another guard in his rage.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alester_Florent\" title=\"Alester Florent\">Alester Florent</a> bends the knee to Stannis, the first of several of Renly's followers to join their late king's brother.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Loras, however, returns to <a href=\"/index.php/Bitterbridge\" title=\"Bitterbridge\">Bitterbridge</a> from Storm's End with a fifth of Renly's knights.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Lords <a href=\"/index.php/Randyll_Tarly\" title=\"Randyll Tarly\">Randyll Tarly</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Mathis_Rowan\" title=\"Mathis Rowan\">Mathis Rowan</a>, who had also accompanied Renly,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok31.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> leave the camp as well.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Fighting\">Fighting</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fighting_at_Bitterbridge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Fighting\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The news of Renly's death reaches Bitterbridge, where near sixty thousand men<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> are encamped and led by lesser lords and commanders of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-SSM_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-SSM-10\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> The camp falls into confusion and conflict as rival envoys arrive, becoming a collection of feudal levies instead of a unified host. Some men return to their homes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-SSM_10-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-SSM-10\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>At some point after Lord Tarly returns to Bitterbridge, a fight breaks out between some who wish to declare for Stannis and some who follow <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a>'s decision not to. Randyll seizes the stores and puts many men—mainly <a href=\"/index.php/House_Florent\" title=\"House Florent\">Florents</a>—to death. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lorent_Caswell\" title=\"Lorent Caswell\">Lorent Caswell</a> locks himself inside his castle to avoid the hostilities.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Parmen_Crane\" title=\"Parmen Crane\">Parmen Crane</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Erren_Florent\" title=\"Erren Florent\">Erren Florent</a>, two knights sent by Stannis to retrieve the army,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> are taken prisoner.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fighting_at_Bitterbridge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Parmen and Erren are taken to <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a> as hostages.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rowan\" title=\"House Rowan\">Rowans</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Oakheart\" title=\"House Oakheart\">Oakhearts</a> are spotted north of the <a href=\"/index.php/Mander\" title=\"Mander\">Mander</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> rides from the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> to Bitterbridge and then Highgarden,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos68.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> negotiating an alliance between the Tyrells, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>, and King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey I Baratheon</a>. Most of the men at Bitterbridge join Joffrey,<sup id=\"cite_ref-SSM_10-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-SSM-10\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> leading to the defeat of Stannis in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fighting_at_Bitterbridge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras</a> is likely making for <a href=\"/index.php/Bitterbridge\" title=\"Bitterbridge\">Bitterbridge</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">His sister</a> is there, <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly's</a> queen, as well as a great many soldiers who suddenly find themselves kingless. Which side will they take now? A ticklish question. Many serve the lords who remained at <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>, and those lords now belong to <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Small_council\" title=\"Small council\">small council</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>It would be hugely overstating to say there was a battle, but there was definitely much confusion and conflict when word reached them of <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End_(299)\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End (299)\">Renly's death</a>. At that point -- and in the days that followed, as rival envoys began to arrive -- Renly's foot ceased to be a whole and became more a gathering of feudal levies, each of which had to make its own decision as to what to do now. Presume some fighting. Presume that a lot of people just decided this might be a swell time to go home. But most of them ultimately wound up with the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">Tyrell</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> alliance.<sup id=\"cite_ref-SSM_10-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-SSM-10\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fighting_at_Bitterbridge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-StannisReach-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-StannisReach_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\">Fossoway of Cider Hall</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_New_Barrel\" title=\"House Fossoway of New Barrel\">Fossoway of New Barrel</a> change their support to Stannis after Renly's death and potentially have men behind at Bitterbridge.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-StannisStorm-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-StannisStorm_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Caron\" title=\"House Caron\">Caron</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Connington\" title=\"House Connington\">Connington</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Errol\" title=\"House Errol\">Errol</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Estermont\" title=\"House Estermont\">Estermont</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Morrigen\" title=\"House Morrigen\">Morrigen</a> change their support to Stannis after Renly's death and potentially have men left behind at Bitterbridge.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Tyrell-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Tyrell_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Ambrose\" title=\"House Ambrose\">Ambrose</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Beesbury\" title=\"House Beesbury\">Beesbury</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackbar\" title=\"House Blackbar\">Blackbar</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bushy\" title=\"House Bushy\">Bushy</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Cuy\" title=\"House Cuy\">Cuy</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dunn\" title=\"House Dunn\">Dunn</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Footly\" title=\"House Footly\">Footly</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">Hightower</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hunt\" title=\"House Hunt\">Hunt</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Inchfield\" title=\"House Inchfield\">Inchfield</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Leygood\" title=\"House Leygood\">Leygood</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Oakheart\" title=\"House Oakheart\">Oakheart</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rowan\" title=\"House Rowan\">Rowan</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Shermer\" title=\"House Shermer\">Shermer</a> support Renly and potentially have men left behind at Bitterbridge.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Fighting_at_Bitterbridge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\">1.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_42\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 42\">Chapter 42</a>, Davos II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\">2.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_44\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 44\">Chapter 44</a>, Tyrion X.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\">3.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\">3.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-3\">3.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-4\">3.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-5\">3.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 36\">Chapter 36</a>, Tyrion VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_K